# Worker Conventions

- `apps/worker/src/index.ts` starts the worker process.
- Temporal workflows and workers live under `apps/worker/src/temporal`.
- Ingestion-specific activities live under `apps/worker/src/temporal/activities/ingestion`.

- When changing worker code:
- keep orchestration logic in workflows
- keep side effects and external calls in activities
- preserve typed workflow inputs and outputs when extending behavior

- Background ingestion behavior should stay in the worker layer, not in API route handlers.
